      <description>&lt;div&gt;Article:&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div&gt;Lobsters:&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;story_content&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;story_text&#34;&gt; &lt;p&gt;What are you doing this week? Feel free to share!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Keep in mind it’s OK to do nothing at all, too.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
      <author>caius</author>
